Class MovieCollection

java.lang.Object
Models.Searchable
Models.MovieCollection
All Implemented Interfaces:
ISearchable
public class MovieCollection extends Searchable
This holds a movie collection that the user has The id ArrayList is from the json file The Models.Movie ArrayList is built from the id ArrayList (use the Models.Movie arraylist for everything)
